high_descs: Head to the knife on the table in front of you.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Bring the knife around to the stove on the other side of the room.
Put the knife in the large pan on the stove.
Pick up the large pan with knife on the stove.
Turn around, bring the pan with knife to the round black table on the left.
Put the pan with knife on the table, left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife in it on the round table.

high_descs: move forwards to the left side of the table ahead, turn right to face that table
grab the knife off of the table there
turn around and walk over to the kitchen stove ahead
place the knife inside the pan on the left side of the stove
grab the pan off of the burner of the stove
turn around and walk over to the table on the left side corner of the kitchen
place the pan down on the kitchen table there
anns.task_desc: place a pan with a knife in it down on the kitchen table

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the counter, then turn right and walk up to the counter, turn right again to face the black table.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle off of the black table.
Turn right and walk towards the white table, then hang a right and walk up to the stove.
Put the knife in the deep metal pan that is on the front left burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal pan with the knife in it off of the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn left and walk up to the round black table.
Put the pan with the knife in it on the table to the left of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a deep pan with a large knife in it on a black table.
